X_n = a_1 + ... + a_n
P(a_n \neq -1 \space i.o) = 0
X_n/n \rightarrow -1 a.s 
X_n \rightarrow -\infty \space a.s
\frac{X_n}{n} \to -1 \quad \text{a.s.}
N=N(\omega)
\left| \frac{X_n(\omega)}{n}- (-1) \right| < \frac{1}{2}
n \geq N
\frac{X_n(\omega)}{n} \leq -\frac{1}{2}
X_n(\omega) \leq - \frac{1}{2} n
n \to \infty
X_n \to - \infty
M>0
|X_n| \leq M
n
\frac{X_n}{n} \to 0
